{"type": "article", "id": 24371, "title": "可固定于车后的狗窝", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-24T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144101PrF9N3X5utREdj0k.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">意大利工作室 D-NAMIC 为宠物狗设计了一个可固定于自行车或摩托车车后的小窝，主体是用塑料做的，里面带有靠背和软垫。特别在于它有一个圆形的孔，可以将头伸出来，当你觉得无暇顾及它的安全时也可以手提着小窝。它有 11 种颜色可选，目前已完成众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/d-namic/pow-pet-on-wheels/description\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021440584Al3cjKhFx8LtSCV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.655\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144058EVsfhYiZBvy7camL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144059FIJtUlndvbR8G5CT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144059punJZa34Oxb8vA2G.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73529412\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144100PUap15Fbg7zqLCNe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}